# Data — NEVER commit raw proprietary data
# Bloomberg and exchange-licensed data are not redistributable.
# Keep all real data files in data/ (ignored). Only data/README.md is tracked.
data/*.csv
data/*.xlsx
data/*.xls
data/*.parquet
data/*.feather
!data/README.md

# Results — regenerated locally; no need to commit by default.
# Exception: the six paper figures are checked in so they render in the README.
results/figures/*.png
results/figures/*.pdf
results/tables/*.csv
!results/figures/1_OLS_Effect_Sizes.png
!results/figures/2_Cross_Correlation_All.png
!results/figures/3_Granger_Causality_All.png
!results/figures/4_Impulse_Response_All.png
!results/figures/5_Rolling_R2_All.png
!results/figures/6_Feature_Importance.png
!results/figures/.gitkeep
!results/tables/.gitkeep

